description:
It was a cold February morning, I was touring the East Coast, USA, this was the middle of the route. We stay for a few days in DC, we play at Black Cat, legendary venue own by Dave Grohl, fact.

The inscription in the wall says 
"IN THIS TEMPLE
AS IN THE HEARTS OF THE PEOPLE
FOR WHOM HE SAVED THE UNION
THE MEMORY OF ABRAHAM LINCOLN
IS ENSHRINED FOREVER"

Lying between the north and south chambers of the open-air Memorial is the central hall, which contains the large solitary figure of Abraham Lincoln.

1/1
